headline: Avery Dennison to Webcast First Quarter 2025 Earnings Conference Call
summary: MENTOR, Ohio, April 03, 2025--Avery Dennison Corporation (NYSE: AVY), a leading global materials science and digital identification solutions company, today announced it will host its first quarter 2025 earnings conference call at 11:00 a.m. ET on Wednesday, April 23, 2025. The company’s first quarter release will be issued that morning at approximately 6:45 a.m. ET.
